\noptical/X-ray correlation, suggesting that irradiation does not play a strong\nrole in the optical, compared to other sources of emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 18:02:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
