on-based power forecasts by comparing simplified physical\nmodels and a machine learning model. This experiment shows that forecasts\nerrors on the synthetic power data are comparable to real-world historical\npower measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2022 13:20:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-04"}
